UPDATE locales_page_Text SET text_loc8='$N represents a new, united front against the Lich King known as the Knights of the Ebon Blade. Yes, majesty, death knights turned against their former master. They are led by the son of Lord Alexandros Mograine - the Ashbringer. They seek what we seek, what we all seek: the end of the Scourge.

I ask not that you accept $N and the Knights of the Ebon Blade into the Alliance, but only that you show tolerance.
