UPDATE locales_page_Text SET text_loc8='Years and years I have been locked away in this magical prison.  Tonight, I make my escape.  I have everything I need to make my break.

<Water smeared ink has ruined this section of the letter>

Why have I been here so long?  What did I do to deserve this?  Days and days of these thoughts running through my head.  What could someone do deserve this?

<Water smeared ink has ruined this section of the letter>

Perhaps I will find out in another life.' WHERE entry=3543; /* text: Years and years I have been locked away in this magical prison.  Tonight, I make my escape.  I have everything I need to make my break.

